This script automatically moves totems into the player's offhand and 9th slot of their hotbar when in inventory. ```def module double-hand-auto-totem
def desc "Custom Scripted Module"

on tick if input_active inventory {
    switch #totem
    gui_quickmove #totem 9
    if off_holding #air {
        gui_swap #totem
    }
}